title: MMYYKK - studio session on The Local Show at The Current
description:
Blending soul, jazz, hip-hop and R&B, MMYYKK and The Blackbeat Theory performed a dynamic, dexterous set of 3 original songs at The Current’s studio. Each talented member of the band plays in various projects throughout the Twin Cities. MMYYKK’s collaborative compositions standout with their poignant message of love, designed to heal, grow and connect. 

Songs played:
00:00 "Sweetest Embrace"
06:00 "Better"
10:31 "Troubled Man"

Personnel:
MMYYKK - keys, vocals
Jalyn Spencer - bass
LA Buckner - drums
Omar Abdulkarim - horn
